data.description:
*NO HOA* Escape to your very own tropical oasis in the heart of Wellington! This luscious 1.1-acre haven boasts all the elements of your dream homestead property with convenient access to premiere shopping, amenities and attractions, you're just a short drive away from everything you need!This Spanish style 2-story home boasts 3 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, a pool with plenty of area for relaxing and entertaining, a recently remodeled kitchen and updated bathrooms. The first floor dazzles with Mexican tile, while the second boasts brand-new LVP flooring. Step outside and discover a botanical wonderland, complete with a charming gazebo beside a serene koi pond. The backyard is cross-fenced, offering ample space for horses or your furry friends. With impact windows and doors, this home is built to withstand it all.

The expansive property also includes a detached 400-square-foot building that can easily be converted into an Airbnb, guest house or gym, as well as a 12x20 roll-up door shed, and if that's not enough throw in a third building that's 24X30 for storage or customization.

With NO HOA, the possibilities are endless.

The property includes a chicken coop with plenty of land for horses and an aviary for birds/ rabbits etc.. Unleash your inner homesteader and enjoy the benefits of farm-fresh eggs just steps away from your kitchen.

If relaxation and recreation are high priorities for you, this home has you covered. Step outside to discover your very own private in-ground pool, the perfect oasis for cooling off on hot summer days or simply lounging in the sun. Immerse yourself in the tranquil ambiance as you admire the lush greenery that surrounds the pool, creating an atmosphere that feels like your very own slice of paradise.

For the adventurous souls, an full RV hook-up with Water and Sewer is ready and waiting. Also, parking for 12 cars. A Drive Thru secured motorcycle, 4 wheeler Bldg with AC. A new metal roof (2020), 2 ACs installed 2019, and two Titan Endless water heaters (2 years old) ensure worry-free living. This is just the beginning of your new life in paradise!
